<A href="http://www.crn.com/news/applications-os/240149346/emc-greenplums-pivotal-hd-aims-to-bring-sql-ease-to-hadoop-big-data.htm">CRN</a> and another still on 		
		<a href="http://siliconangle.com/blog/2013/02/25/does-the-world-need-another-hadoop-distro-greenplum-says-yes/"><EM>Silicon Angle</EM></a>.  
 </LI>
 
 
 <LI>  <A href= "http://www.springone2gx.com/conference/santa_clara/2013/09/home">SpringOne2GX 2013 has been announced</a>! 
